list.title: Black
list.product_info:
Put your memories on display in the most simply beautiful way. Our Everyday Memories frame adds a picture-perfect finishing touch to any room. Just choose the perfect size and color to complement your favorite photo!

  • Strikingly simple, eye-catching frame complements any décor
  • Available in black, white, espresso or light rustic gray
  • Made of durable MDF wood with a wood-grain effect
  • Beautifully displays one 4x6″ photo on a table or desk; wall options available as well
  • Variety of sizes available

list.title: Gallery of Memories
list.product_info:
So many memories to share! Why create a gallery wall from scratch when you can display your favorite photos in a stunning collage frame? This easy-to-hang gallery display shows off five photos in the most beautifully pre-arranged way.

  • Gallery-style design creates a focal point for any room
  • Features five openings to hold favorite photos
  • Openings are different sizes to ensure a perfect fit
  • 2 4x6″ photos, 1 5x7″ photo, and 2 5x5″ photos
  • Measures 19.7″W x 16.9″H x 1.3″D

list.title: This Is Us
list.product_info:
It’s the simple moments in life that mean the most. Capture your favorite memories in the most rustic-chic way. Photos are securely clipped to a clothes-line style string and can easily be switched out, reminding everyone that “This Is Us.”

  • Heartfelt display for cherished memories
  • Rustic wooden finished frame
  • Includes clips and string for hanging photos
  • Designed for 4x6″, 5x5″ and 5x7″ photos
  • Measures 21.2″W x 9.2″H x 1.5″D

list.title: Gallery of Memories (White)
list.product_info:

  • Features eight individual 4x6″ photo openings
  • Made of all-white wood and standard glass
  • Measures 24.6″W x 13″H x 1.3″D

list.title: Happily Forever After
list.product_info:
This collage-style wedding frame is the perfect way to relive your special day. Featuring 8 inserts to display your favorite photos and elegant silver accents, it’s a beautiful reminder of your “Happily Forever After”.

  • Large, white collage-style frame features silver inlay
  • Center of the frame reads “Happily Forever After” in silver foil
  • Elegantly displays eight 4x6″ photos
  • Includes 2 sturdy sawtooth hangars for easy installation
  • Designed from wood and standard glass
  • Measures 20.25″W x 20.25″H x 0.813″D

list.title: So Many Memories (Black)
list.product_info:
So many memories, so many photos! How could you possibly choose only one? Share favorite moments spent with special people, photos from a milestone celebration or memories from a once-in-a-lifetime trip. This contemporary, montage-style frame complements any decor.

  • Versatile gallery design shows off cherished memories
  • Contemporary, durable frame made of PS injection wood-plastic composite
  • Available in Black
  • Holds 12 4x6″ photos
  • Measures 24.5″W x 24.25″H x 1.25″D

list.title: Graduation Tassel
list.product_info:
This Photo & Tassel graduation frame features a shadowbox-inspired design to showcase the accomplishments of the new graduate. Add a celebratory photo from graduation day and display their class tassel from the silver button-tab hangar.

  • Perfect graduation gift for parents, grandparents and graduates
  • Black shadowbox frame features a white border and area to hang tassel
  • Beautifully displays any 5x7″ photo
  • Includes a sturdy sawtooth wall hangar for easy placement
  • Made of wood and standard glass
  • Measures 11″W x 12.25″H x 1.5″D

list.title: Letterboard
list.product_info:
Trendy and fun, this stylish frame includes a letterboard for custom messages. Featuring space for a favorite photo, it’s a playful way to celebrate everything from weddings and new babies to graduations, anniversaries, family vacations and more.

  • Rustic, gray frame with letterboard area for personalization
  • Includes 294 1” letters, numbers and symbols
  • Sweetly displays any 4x6″ photo
  • Display options include an easel for tabletops or a triangle hanger for walls
  • Designed from wood and standard glass
  • Measures 12.5″W x 8.3″H x .8″D

list.title: Newborn Baby Prints
list.product_info:
Welcome the new arrival with this shadowbox-style frame! Showcase a favorite photo and a timeless imprint of baby’s hand or foot. An acid-free beveled mat and reversible background mat are included, along with soft clay for a perfect impression.

  • White shadowbox frame with reversible pink and blue background mat
  • Includes soft, air-drying clay, ruler, double-sided tape and instructions
  • Sweetly displays any 4x6″ photo
  • Features an easel for display on any desk or table
  • Designed from wood/standard glass and is 100% safe for newborns
  • Measures 5.875″H x 7.875″W x .625″D

list.title:
My Whole Heart,
for My Whole Life
list.product_info:
This square white frame is a sweet, sentimental reminder of the day you said, “I do”. Stylishly surround a favorite photo of your wedding day with a beautifully scripted message that celebrates your commitment to forever.

  • White square frame displays a cherished photo
  • Gray mat includes “my whole heart for my whole life” in script font
  • Elegantly displays one 5x5″ photo
  • Display options include an easel for tabletops or a sawtooth hangar for walls
  • Designed from wood and standard glass
  • Measures: 10″W x 10″H x .6″D

list.title: Thumbprint Heart
list.product_info:
This square white frame is an elegant way to feature a favorite photo from your wedding day. Add your fingerprints in the shape of a heart to the white matting for a personal touch. The silver accents are a stylish complement to any décor.

  • Silver frame features white matting with silver background mat
  • Center of mat reads “Mr. and Mrs.” in silver
  • Displays one 4x6″ photo. Includes clean-touch ink pad for fingerprints
  • Include an easel for tabletop display or a hangar for walls
  • Designed from wood and standard glass
  • Measures 8.125″W x 8.125″H x .688″D

list.title: Pawprints
list.product_info:
Capture and display your pet’s paw print and photo with this hinged, shadowbox-style frame. Its modern, gray distressed details are complemented by an acid-free white beveled mat. Soft clay is included for a perfect impression.

  • Gray distressed shadowbox-style frame with white mat and gray background board
  • Includes soft, air-drying clay, ruler, double-sided tape and instructions
  • Sweetly displays any 4x6″ photo
  • Hinged frame easily sits on any table or desk
  • Designed from wood/standard glass and 100% Pet Safe
  • Measures 12.75″W x 7.5″H x 1.37″D
